text: Jozef Menich (born 15 September 1994) is a Slovak footballer who plays as a defender for FC ViOn Zlaté Moravce. ==Club career== ===MFK Ružomberok=== Menich made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for RužomberokSpartak Myjava - MFK Ružomberok 1:3 06.08.2016, futbalnet.sk against Spartak Myjava on 6 August 2016. ==References== ==External links== * MFK Ružomberok official club profile * * Futbalnet profile Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:MFK Lokomotíva Zvolen players Category:MFK Ružomberok players Category:ŠKF iClinic Sereď players Category:FC Spartak Trnava players Category:FC ViOn Zlaté Moravce players Category:Slovak Super Liga players
